\c 13
\s Amazibulo ehlukaniselwa iN\nd kosi\nd*; umkhosi wesinkwa esingelamvubelo
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Ngingcwelisela lonke izibulo, elivula loba yisiphi isizalo phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli, elomuntu lelenyamazana, lingelami\x + 13.12,13,15; 34.19. Nani 8.16; 18.15,17. 22.29,30. Levi 27.26. Nani 3.13; 8.16,17. Dute. 15.19. Hez. 44.30. Luka 2.23.\x*.
\p
\v 3 UMozisi wasesithi ebantwini: Khumbulani lolusuku eliphume ngalo eGibhithe, endlini yobugqili\x + 12.42. Dute. 16.3.\x*; ngoba ngamandla esandla iN\nd kosi\nd* ilikhuphile lapha. Njalo kakungadliwa isinkwa esilemvubelo\x + 12.8.\x*.
\v 4 Ngalolusuku liyaphuma ngenyanga kaAbhibhi\x + 12.2. Neh. 2.1. Esta 3.7.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Njalo kuzakuthi lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* isikungenisile elizweni lamaKhanani lamaHethi lamaAmori lamaHivi lamaJebusi\x + 3.8,17; 23.23; 33.2; 34.11. Dute. 7.1. & 20.17. Josh. 3.10; 12.8; 24.11. Hlu. 3.5. So Gen. 15.19,20.\x*, afunga kuboyihlo ukukunika lona\x + 13.11; 6.8.\x*, ilizwe eligeleza uchago loluju\x + 3.8.\x*, uzagcina linkonzo ngalinyanga\x + 12.25,26.\x*.
\v 6 Insuku eziyisikhombisa uzakudla izinkwa ezingelamvubelo, langosuku lwesikhombisa kuzakuba khona umkhosi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 12.15,16.\x*.
\v 7 Izinkwa ezingelamvubelo zizadliwa ngensuku eziyisikhombisa; njalo kakuyikubonwa kuwe okuvutshelweyo lemvubelo kayiyikubonwa kuwe kuwo wonke umngcele wakho.
\p
\v 8 Njalo uzatshela indodana yakho ngalolosuku usithi: Ngenxa yalokho iN\nd kosi\nd* eyakwenza kimi ekuphumeni kwami eGibhithe\x + 13.14; 12.26.\x*.
\v 9 Futhi kuzakuba kuwe luphawu phezu kwesandla sakho\x + 13.16. Dute. 6.8; 11.18. Nani 15.39. Mat. 23.5.\x* lesikhumbuzo\x + 12.14.\x* phakathi laphakathi kwamehlo akho, ukuze umlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* ube semlonyeni wakho; ngoba ngesandla esilamandla iN\nd kosi\nd* ikukhuphile eGibhithe.
\v 10 Ngakho uzagcina lesisimiso ngesikhathi saso esimisiweyo iminyaka ngeminyaka\x + 12.14,17,24,43.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Njalo kuzakuthi lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* isikungenisile elizweni lamaKhanani, njengokufunga kwayo kuwe lakuboyihlo, isikunike lona,
\v 12 uzakwehlukanisela iN\nd kosi\nd* konke okuvula isizalo; lalo lonke izibulo lomqegu wezifuyo olazo, amaduna azakuba ngaweN\nd kosi\x + 13.2.\x*\nd*.
\v 13 Lalo lonke izibulo likababhemi uzalihlenga ngewundlu\x + 34.20.\x*; kodwa uba ungalihlengi, uzalephula intamo; lalo lonke izibulo lomuntu phakathi kwamadodana akho uzalihlenga\x + Nani 3.46,47; 18.15,16.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Njalo kuzakuthi lapho indodana yakho ikubuza ngesikhathi esizayo isithi: Kuyini lokhu\x + 12.26.\x*? Uzakuthi kuyo: Ngamandla esandla iN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhupha eGibhithe, endlini yobugqili\x + 13.3,16.\x*.
\v 15 Ngoba kwathi uFaro ezenza lukhuni ukuthi asiyekele sihambe, iN\nd kosi\nd* yabulala lonke izibulo elizweni leGibhithe\x + 12.29.\x*, kusukela kuzibulo lomuntu kusiya kuzibulo lezifuyo; ngakho ngiyahlabela iN\nd kosi\nd* konke okuvula isizalo okuduna; kodwa lonke izibulo lamadodana ami ngiyalihlenga\x + 13.13.\x*.
\v 16 Njalo kuzakuba luphawu phezu kwesandla sakho \w lamafilakteriyu\w** phakathi laphakathi kwamehlo akho\x + 13.9.\x*, ngoba ngamandla esandla iN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhupha eGibhithe.
\s Ukuhamba kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli besiya eLwandle lweMihlanga
\p
\v 17 Kwasekusithi uFaro eseyekele abantu bahambe, uNkulunkulu kabakhokhelanga \add nge\add*ndlela yelizwe lamaFilisti, lanxa yayiseduze; ngoba uNkulunkulu wathi: Hlezi abantu bazisole nxa bebona impi, babuyele eGibhithe\x + 14.11,12. Nani 14.1-4.\x*.
\v 18 Kodwa uNkulunkulu wababhodisa abantu ngendlela yenkangala yoLwandle oluBomvu\x + 14.2.\x*. Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesenyuka besuka elizweni leGibhithe behlomile.
\v 19 UMozisi wasethatha amathambo kaJosefa wahamba lawo, ngoba wayebafungisile lokubafungisa abantwana bakoIsrayeli esithi: Isibili uNkulunkulu uzalihambela; futhi kalibokwenyusa lapha amathambo ami lihambe lawo\x + Gen. 50.25. Josh. 24.32. Seb. 7.16.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Basebesuka eSukothi, bamisa inkamba eEthama, ekucineni kwenkangala\x + 12.37. Nani 33.6.\x*.
\v 21 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasihamba phambi kwabo emini ngensika yeyezi ukubakhokhela endleleni, lebusuku ngensika yomlilo ukubakhanyisela\x + 14.19,24; 40.38. Nani 9.15; 10.34; 14.14. Dute. 1.33. Neh. 9.12,19. Hlab. 78.14; 99.7; 105.39. Isa. 4.5. 1 Kor. 10.1.\x*, ukuze bahambe emini lebusuku.
\v 22 Kayiyisusanga insika yeyezi emini, lensika yomlilo ebusuku, phambi kwabantu.
